item.title: Matthew Perry Recreates Friends Trip to Las Vegas in Rare Photo
item.description: Could he BE any more like Chandler? Matthew Perry took a trip to Las Vegas with his friends over the weekend — unintentionally recreating an infamous episode of his hit NBC series. “Vegas with old friends this weekend,” Perry, 54, captioned a photo via Instagram on Monday, June 27. “This photo was taken minutes before we went downstairs and lost every dime any of us have ever earned.” The snap, which features Perry posing with a few pals during a recent trip to Sin City, inevitably reminded fans of the actor’s infamous 1999 Friends two-part episode, where Perry’s character Chandler Bing and his girlfriend Monica Gellar (Courtney Cox) fly to Vegas and debate tying the knot.

item.title: Shaq As An Undercover Lyft Driver Is Proof There's Still Good In The World

Clara and Valentino share the same parents, and she is the younger sister to Valentino. Valentino reportedly also has a younger half-brother Luca Marini. Clara was born to her mother, Stefania Rossi, and her father, Graziano Rossi. Further, she shares the same Italian ancestry as her brother and carves a White Caucasian ethnicity.

item.title: Where is Steve Patterson From Twin Cities Live Going? Everything On His Salary & More
item.description: A co-host of ‘Twin Cities Live’, Steve Patterson, is leaving the show in near future, but where is he going? Steve Patterson is a co-host of the popular show, ‘Two Cities Live’. His co-host of the show is Elizabeth Ries. The program is telecasted every day from 3-4:30 p.m on KSTP. He also hosts another show entitled Donna and Steve Show on MyTalk 107.1 on the Radio. He had studied at Azusa Pacific University in Southern California and graduated with a degree in Communication Studies.

item.title: Etta Ng Chok Lam Biography, Age, Wiki, Height, Weight, Boyfriend, Family & More
item.description: Etta Ng Chok Lam has earned the limelight for being the estranged daughter of the popular actor Jackie Chan. She became popular for being conceived as a result of Jackie Chan’s illicit relationship with Elaine Ng Yi-Lei. Though his father accepted the relationship but avoided the responsibility of the child. Neither she met Jackie nor did he take an initiative to support her financially. Etta Ng Chok Lam stands 170 cm or 5 feet and 7 inches tall.

item.title: Famous TV Hosts and Their Sidekicks: Ellen, tWitch, More
item.description: Dynamic duos! It’s hard to imagine some of the biggest TV hosts carrying on without their beloved sidekicks. The Ellen DeGeneres Show felt right at home when Stephen “tWitch” Boss joined in 2014 as its in-house DJ. Their on-screen bond later led to tWitch being featured as Ellen DeGeneres’ sidekick and announcer on Ellen’s Game of Games, which premiered in 2017. As reports of the show’s alleged toxic on-set environment surfaced, tWitch stood by DeGeneres and came to her defense.

item.title: Former Bodybuilder Posts Stunning Transformation Photos
item.description: Jolene Jones, a former body bodybuilder from Kalispell, Montana, used to obsessively count grams of proteins, carbs and fats. “To get competition ready I was really limited,” the 26-year-old tells Us Weekly exclusively. “No alcohol, no beef, no wheat, no sugar and no dairy. I would have chicken with broccoli for lunch every day and it got to the point where I would gag and have to chug water to get it down.

item.title: Geno Smith Signs 4-Year Contract With New York Jets
item.description: It’s official, Geno Smith is a Jet. The standout West Virginia University quarterback signed his rookie contract with the New York Jets today (July 22) solidifying his second major contract since being drafted. Smith will reportedly earn $5 million through four years and is expected to compete with Mark Sanchez for a starting position at quarterback. Over the weekend, Smith confidently told reporters he has a “great shot” at winning the starting role an that he is already comfortable with the team’s play book.

item.title: Jaleel White Believes Hollywood Doesn't Honor Youth Actors
item.description: While the 2017 Emmy Awards provided a load of winning moments for people of color within and outside the entertainment world, there was still room for valid critiques regarding the underrepresented. This time, instead of women or people of color, it was children who received the cold shoulder. Despite its popular status and vocal fan base, Netflix top show Stranger Things did not take home any major Emmy awards of the evening (best drama, best supporting actor, best supporting actress).

item.title: The Best Amazon Black Friday Deals Out Now Up to 92% Off
item.description: Us Weekly has affiliate partnerships. We receive compensation when you click on a link and make a purchase. Learn more! It’s begun! The Amazon 2023 Black Friday event is here, and it lasts through November 24 (with Cyber Monday deals to follow)! We’re seeing deals up to and even over 90% off in this week-long Black Friday sale. You could save hundreds on a single item! Of course, we need to move fast, so let’s get to it.

item.title: Tom Selleck Didn't Have The Easiest Time On Friends, But Jennifer Aniston Seems To Disagree
item.description: Appearing on Friends was a career-altering opportunity. However, for the actors that did take part, it was at times a very nervous experience, especially given the chemistry of the main cast. The likes of Jennifer Coolidge admitted to keeping a low profile during their time on the show, given how tight the main cast was. RELATED - Friends Fans Noticed A Fake Rachel In A Scene With Joey When They Changed The Size Ratio Of The Episode As we'll reveal in the following, Tom Selleck's experience on the show was also one that had some elevated levels of anxiety.

item.description: Who is Nigo? Tobaki Niga, known professionally as Nigo, is a Japanese fashion designer and entrepreneur best known as the founder of A Bathing Ape. This famous streetwear brand gained a cult following in the late 1990s and early 2000s. Nigo’s innovative designs, which blend Japanese aesthetics with Western pop culture influences, have significantly impacted street fashion and hip-hop culture. Over the years, Nigo has expanded his brand empire, launching several other successful clothing lines and collaborating with notable brands such as Adidas and Coca-Cola.

item.title: Katy Perry Must Testify If She Wants To Keep $15 Million Home Amid Lawsuit
item.description: Highlights Key takeaways: Katy Perry will have to testify in a trial regarding the disputed purchase of her $15 million mansion with Orlando Bloom. The seller claims he was mentally incapacitated and did not want to sell the estate, leading to the ongoing lawsuit. Katy and Orlando are also countersuing for over $5 million in damages and expenses due to loss of rental income during the legal proceedings.

item.title: Lalo Rodriguez A Salsa Singer Passed Away At The Age Of 64
item.description: Lalo Rodriguez, a notable vocalist, and guitarist died on December 13 at 64 years old. Cops tracked down his body close to Sabana Abajo in Carolina, Puerto Rico. The Organization of Legal Sciences announced that there was no indication of viciousness on Rodriguez’s body. At the point when specialists showed up on the scene in the wake of getting a report about a dead cadaver, the vocalist was lethargic. Despite the fact that Lalo was entangled in a ton of legitimate troubles because of his medication and liquor fixation, it is questionable whether they had any impact on his passing.

item.title: Retired Police Officer Shares Tupac Shakurs Alleged Last Words
item.description: In September, it will have been 18 years since West Coast lyricist Tupac departed this Earth. There are still unsolved mysteries surrounding the day he died, but one police officer alleges that he witnessed Pac’s last words. The now-retired Chris Carroll of the Las Vegas police department was the first cop on the scene once the rapper was shot. In a piece for Vegas Seven, he details those last moments. Here is an excerpt:

item.title: Speculation on Bobby Roode and Eric Youngs Futures, Dusty Rhodes Classic Returning?, Jake Roberts
item.description: Speculation on Bobby Roode and Eric Young’s FuturesAccording to Dave Meltzer of Wrestling Observer Radio, there are rumors that the TNA departures of Eric Young and Bobby Roode might be WWE related, however talks with WWE have yet to be confirmed. Dusty Rhodes Classic Returning? Cody Rhodes posted the following on his personal Twitter account: Each year. You can’t build enough trophies or monuments high enough for Dad. He was a hero and he was my hero.

item.title: A Glance At Colin Farrells Incredible Acting Career In Hollywood
item.description: Quick LinksRising From The Streets Of Dublin From Ireland To LA Farrell's Transition from Indie Films To Epic Blockbusters Colin Farrell's Critically Acclaimed Performances Farrell's Other Accomplishments:  Colin Farrell is a multi-talented Irish actor who has been captivating audiences with his performances for over two decades. From his breakout role in the hit film Tigerland to his recent work in critically acclaimed projects like The Lobster and Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them, Farrell has consistently proved himself to be one of the most versatile and compelling actors of his generation.

item.title: Damian Hurley Biography, Age, Wiki, Height, Weight, Girlfriend, Family & More
item.description: Damian Hurley is a model and actor from England who is popular for being Elizabeth Hurley and Steve Bing’s son. Born to a gorgeous actress and model, Damian even inherited his mother’s beauty. In his life, his father had no major part to play and Damian was brought up as a single mother by Elizabeth Hurley. A very close bond is shared by the mother-son couple, though he also takes a lot from his mother.

item.title: DJ Envy, Eboni K. Williams Debate Men And "Mediocrity" In Dating
item.description: The Breakfast Club‘s DJ Envy and lawyer/author Eboni K. Williams got into a heated exchange on Thursday (May 4) over her viral interview with Iyanla Vanzant about “dating a bus driver.” While sitting in as a guest on the now BET-partnered radio show, Williams explained her stance on why she wouldn’t date the everyday worker. Her initial sentiments, which were that she would only date a bus driver, “if he owns the bus,” caused much debate online, with some agreeing and others criticizing her thoughts.

item.title: Jennifer Lawrence Goes Without Underwear at Oscars Party: Top Stories
item.description: Jennifer Lawrence goes without underwear, Kim Novak looks unrecognizable, and Scarlett Johansson is pregnant: See Us Weekly's top 5 stories from Monday, March 3 in the roundup. 1. Jennifer Lawrence Goes Without Underwear in Edgy Tom Ford Frock at Vanity Fair Oscars Party: Picture J. Law's ready to party! Jennifer Lawrence turned up the sex appeal at the Vanity Fair Oscars bash on Sunday, March 2, trading her sleek red carpet Dior Haute Couture gown for an edgy Tom Ford mini that required her to go without underwear at the annual Graydon Carter-hosted event.

The southern rap legends believe that this is an attack on the genre, and shows that Hip-Hop is not valued as art in the same way other mediums are. In a ComplexCon panel titled “The War On Rap,” TIP and the UGK member joined journalist and lawyer Ari Melber this past Saturday (Nov.

item.title: 15 Things About Rory Gilmore's Romantic Relationships We Never Understood
item.description: Before we start getting into all of the many confusing aspects of Rory Gilmore's love life, we will say that we love Rory to bits. The entire Gilmore Girl series is a real masterpiece and that's largely due to how amazing Lorelai and Rory were both written and played. That being said, the more we rewatch this show, the harder it becomes to ignore all of the issues surrounding Rory and her many relationships.

item.title: AJ Francis (Top Dolla) Releases Song Thank You // 89 Days To Address His WWE Release
item.description: says he’s got 89 days before he makes another splash in the professional wrestling industry. AJ Francis, aka Top Dolla of Hit Row, was released by WWE on Thursday, November 18. Francis, Swerve Scott and Ashante Adonis were three of the eight names cut by WWE, with budget cuts being cited as the reason for the move. On Friday, he posted a new track called “Thank You // 89 Days” to comment on his release and address his future in the wrestling industry.

item.title: Christine Governale Height, Weight, Net Worth, Age, Birthday, Wikipedia, Who, Nationality, Biography
item.description: Sal Governale is a stockbroker, radio character, jokester, and author who has showed up on Howard’s show. Governale is likewise perceived for being an individual from the Stern program and for having a decent connection with Richard Cristy. His own life has been revealed, as has his gay relationship with Richard, which has started contention. Sal Denies has expressed that he is hitched and has a mysterious relationship with another man.

item.title: CNN Paid Don Lemon A Fortune Before He Was Fired, But The Same Can't Be Said For One Of His Female C
item.description: Don Lemon is an American television journalist who served as a CNN anchor from 2014 until 2023. That is until he was dismissed by the mega-multinational news network for making controversial comments about women. During his early career as a journalist, Lemon hosted weekend news programs on local television stations in Alabama and Pennsylvania. Climbing the ranks, he most recently co-hosted CNN This Morning with Kaitlan Collins and Poppy Harlow before being fired in April 2023.

item.description: On a recent episode of Grilling JR with Conrad Thompson, Jim Ross shared his thoughts on the late Giant Gonzalez, who JR worked with during the wrestler’s time as El Gigante. JR gives his insight as to why Gonzalez was not successful in the squared circle and also talks about the unfortunate financial trouble he faced post wrestling career. Some quotes from the episode are below as well as the audio clip from Grilling JR.

item.title: Can torque to yield bolts be reused
item.description: How many times can torque-to-yield bolts be used? * Never reuse a torque-to-yield bolt. item.title: Who Is Samuel L. Jackson's Wife And How Did They Meet?
item.description: Samuel L. Jackson is one of the highest-grossing movie stars of all time, appearing in Pulp Fiction, Goodfellas, Star Wars, Jurassic Park, and The Avengers. Jackson is considered one of the most honest and exceptionally authentic actors in Hollywood. He is one of those celebrities that people love to see both on and off-screen. Movie legend Samuel L. Jackson has been married to actress and producer LaTanya Richardson for nearly 40 years.

item.title: Will Smith Responds to Jada Pinkett Smiths 2016 Oscar Boycott
item.description: Next time a heads-up would be good! No one was more surprised by Jada Pinkett Smith’s call to boycott the 2016 Oscars than her husband, Will Smith. “I was out of the country at the time, and I came home [and said], ‘What happened?’” the Concussion star, 47, revealed on Good Morning America Thursday, January 21. “She’s deeply passionate, and when she’s moved, she has to go. I heard her words, and I was knocked over.

item.title: Beyonce Wore an Actual Wedding Dress at the 2016 VMAs
item.description: Here comes the winner! Beyoncé wore a wedding dress — her third look of the night — to accept a Moonman for Video of the Year at the 2016 MTV Video Music Awards on Sunday, August 28. The Lemonade singer, 34, stunned in a Yolan Cris Couture Calamo wedding dress from the Spanish designer’s latest bridal collection. The floor-skimming number was made of floral lace and featured a low neckline and diaphanous puff sleeves.

During an appearance on the Wednesday, April 24, episode of Minnie Driver’s “Minnie Questions” podcast, Cox said she regretted giving Coco, now 19, too much freedom to make her own decisions. “I should have [trusted] myself and I should have stepped in,” Cox, 59, said. “I’m not saying I made her who she is, but you do see things in other people —whether it’s just always taking care of people and being the nicest person.

She competed during the show’s twelfth season, winning a $500,000 prize package. She was born on December 17, 1988 in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. She attended Moore College of Art and Design, graduating in 2010 with a Bachelor of Fine Arts degree in Fashion Design.

item.title: Study Sheds New Light on Russias Dyatlov Pass Mountain Mystery
item.description: The mysterious deaths of nine young hikers in the winter of 1959 at a remote pass in the Ural mountains has fascinated Russia for decades and spawned countless theories from aliens to a botched nuclear test. Now research published Thursday in the journal Communications Earth and Environment has added weight to a natural explanation for the deaths of the experienced mountaineers, whose frozen bodies were found scattered across the snowy landscape, some with terrible injuries.

item.description: Robert L. Arrington (born October 19, 1938) is an American philosopher who specialises in moral philosophy, the philosophy of Ludwig Wittgenstein, and the philosophy of psychology. He received his Ph.D. from the University of California, Berkeley. Arrington was born in Bainbridge, Georgia, and received his education at Vanderbilt University (B.A. 1960, with honours) and Tulane University (M.A. 1960, with honours) (M.A. 1962 and Ph.D. 1966). In 1963, after three years as an assistant professor at The University of Southern Mississippi (1963–1966), Arrington accepted a position at Georgia State University, where he is now professor emeritus of philosophy and director of the Wittgenstein Institute.
